Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.48,0:22:31.95,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\bord2\fad(10,10)\pos(516,269)\3c&HE954E9&}真唯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.62,0:22:32.70,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 最後一招下得真有氣勢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.93,0:22:33.65,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.62,0:22:34.41,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\fad(10,250)\bord2\pos(249,380)\3c&HDC0000&}優希對了!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.09,0:22:37.75,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 這樣就可以把這些子都提走了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.75,0:22:37.75,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\3c&HDC0000&\bord2\pos(200,422)}這招就叫做{\3c&H2221EE&}「困鶴巢」!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.78,0:22:39.54,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼這次該怎麼下呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.95,0:22:40.17,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.29,0:22:43.13,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\bord2\fad(10,10)\pos(295,382)\3c&HEB49EB&}這次由真唯來挑戰!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.76,0:22:44.05,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.50,0:22:49.42,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\3c&H2221EE&\bord2\an7\pos(380,343)\fad(350,134)}當左右棋形一樣時\N多數情況下中間的地方就是急所
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.46,0:22:48.17,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.38,0:22:50.93,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就可以很順利地救出白子了
